snippet.title: Urban Myth Dissolution Center - Announcement Trailer | PS5 Games
snippet.description:
https://store.playstation.com/concept/10010358

Unlock the mysteries on PS5! The occult adventure game you’ve been waiting for is coming to PlayStation 5! 

Work alongside the psychic Director of the Urban Myth Dissolution Center to investigate cursed artifacts, haunted properties, and mind-bending dimensional rifts. 

#ps5 #ps5games #UrbanMythDissolusionCenter
